{"ja396:0.1":"Jataka ","ja396:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","ja396:0.3":"Kukkuvagga ","ja396:0.4":"1. Kukkujataka ","ja396:1.1":"“Diyaddhakukku udayena kannika, ","ja396:1.2":"Vidatthiyo attha parikkhipanti nam; ","ja396:1.3":"Sa simsapa saramaya aphegguka, ","ja396:1.4":"Kuhim thita upparito na dhamsati”. ","ja396:2.1":"“Ya timsati saramaya anujjuka, ","ja396:2.2":"Parikiriya gopanasiyo samam thita; ","ja396:2.3":"Tahi susangahita balasa pilita, ","ja396:2.4":"Samam thita upparito na dhamsati. ","ja396:3.1":"Evampi mittehi dalhehi pandito, ","ja396:3.2":"Abhejjarupehi sucihi mantibhi; ","ja396:3.3":"Susangahito siriya na dhamsati, ","ja396:3.4":"Gopanasi bharavahava kannika. ","ja396:4.1":"Kharattacam bellam yathapi satthava, ","ja396:4.2":"Anamasantopi karoti tittakam; ","ja396:4.3":"Samaharam sadum karoti patthiva, ","ja396:4.4":"Asadum kayira tanubandhamuddharam. ","ja396:5.1":"Evampi gamanigamesu pandito, ","ja396:5.2":"Asahasam rajadhanani sangharam; ","ja396:5.3":"Dhammanuvatti patipajjamano, ","ja396:5.4":"Sa phati kayira avihethayam param. ","ja396:6.1":"Odatamulam sucivarisambhavam, ","ja396:6.2":"Jatam yatha pokkharanisu ambujam; ","ja396:6.3":"Padumam yatha agginikasiphalimam, ","ja396:6.4":"Na kaddamo na rajo na vari limpati. ","ja396:7.1":"Evampi voharasucim asahasam, ","ja396:7.2":"Visuddhakammantamapetapapakam; ","ja396:7.3":"Na limpati kammakilesa tadiso, ","ja396:7.4":"Jatam yatha pokkharanisu ambujan”ti. ","ja396:8.1":"Kukkujatakam pathamam. "}